---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "@consts";
---

<BaseLayout title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Nourished Journeys">
  <article class="prose mx-auto dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>About Nourished Journeys</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to Nourished Journeys, a place for calm, thoughtful reflection. Here you'll find resources for journaling, meditation, breath work, yoga, and mindfulness practices.</p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe in the power of daily practices to transform lives. Whether you're seeking clarity through journaling, peace through meditation, or vitality through breath work and yoga, we're here to guide your journey.</p>
    
    <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Journaling</strong> - Techniques to process thoughts, set intentions, and track personal growth</li>
      <li><strong>Meditation</strong> - Guided practices for focus, relaxation, and inner peace</li>
      <li><strong>Breath Work</strong> - Breathing techniques to reduce stress and increase energy</li>
      <li><strong>Yoga</strong> - Physical practices connecting body, mind, and spirit</li>
      <li><strong>Mindfulness</strong> - Present-moment awareness techniques for daily life</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>We hope these resources help you on your path to wellness and self-discovery.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
